data.description: Open House Saturday 12/16 2-4 pm.  **Stunning** traditional home with tons of natural light, a spacious living room open to the dining room. The home also features an open-concept kitchen and family room.  The kitchen boasts generous counter space and a nook making cooking and entertaining a delight. The connecting family room has a fireplace and slider that lead to the serene backyard with 2 covered decks and a 2021 shed. The upstairs has 3 bedrooms and an office or 4 bedrooms, including an expansive main bedroom and suite with dual sinks, a shower, and a walk-in closet. 2023 Roof with warranty, aesthetically updated fireplace with a new pilot, newer laminate flooring, and much more. [Home Energy Score = 3. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10222685]
